## Top Begriffe nach Thema

#### Erweiterte Modellauswertung: Beta-Matrix

::: {style="font-size: smaller"}


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Create top terms
top_terms <- td_beta %>%
  arrange(beta) %>%
  group_by(topic) %>%
  top_n(7, beta) %>%
  arrange(-beta) %>%
  select(topic, term) %>%
  summarise(terms = list(term)) %>%
  mutate(terms = map(terms, paste, collapse = ", ")) %>% 
  unnest(cols = c(terms))

# Output
top_terms %>% 
  head(15)
```

